title: 'Grave doubts' about Donald Trump as commander in chief
text: Former Florida Gov. Jeb Bush said Sunday he has "grave doubts" about whether GOP presidential nomination rival Donald Trump is fit to be president. In an interview on CNN's " State of the Union, " Mr. Bush said Mr. Trump, who leads the Republican presidential primary field, is not a serious candidate ... ...
